[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Cuando la señal de control es 0, la salida está conectada a la entrada 0
[ENGLISH]When the control signal is 0, the output signal is connected to the input 0
[END_LIST]
[IMG]P015_Expl3.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Cuando la señal de control es 1, la salida está conectada a la entrada 1
[ENGLISH]When the control signal is 1, the output signal is connected to the input 1
[END_LIST]
[IMG]P015_Expl4.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Cuando la señal de control es 2, la salida está conectada a la entrada 2
[ENGLISH]When the control signal is 2, the output signal is connected to the input 2
[END_LIST]
[IMG]P015_Expl5.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Cuando la señal de control es 3, la salida está conectada a la entrada 3
[ENGLISH]When the control signal is 3, the output signal is connected to the input 3
[END_LIST]
[IMG]P015_Expl6.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]En este proyecto usarás un multiplexor de 1 bit. Tendrá 2 entradas
[ENGLISH]In this project a 1-bit multiplexor is used. It has 2 inputs
[END_LIST]
[BLOCK_END]

